            <p>Cases that are on the docket at the Supreme Court could shrink as a result of policy shifts after Donald Trump takes office in January. The same goes for dockets at lower federal courts. These include cases involving immigration matters, the Affordable Care Act, climate change, and LGBT rights, many of which arose from Obama administration executive actions and legal interpretations.</p>
